==Latin==

===Etymology===
[[dicto]] ("to say often"), from [[dico]] ("to say") + noun ending [[-io#Latin|-io]] ("-ion")

===Pronunciation===
*Reconstructed classical: /ˈdiktioː/
*Traditional Italian ("ecclesiastical") style: /ˈdiktsio/
*Traditional English style: /ˈdɪkʃ(ɪ)o/

===Noun===
'''dictĭō''' {{f}} (''genitive:'' [[Appendix:Latin third declension|dictĭōnis]])

# saying, speaking, talk, oratory

